    "description": "<i>Through me you pass into the city of woe<br>                                                                                                                                                                                         Through me you pass into eternal pain<br>                                                                                                                                                                                         Through me among the people lost for aye.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Dante Alighieri, The Divine Comedy: Hell,CantoIII</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/c923d574f9a69907fc6f8dcd0d84a96a.avif?t=1602004954\" width=610 height=85 /></span><br>Mortido is an action-adventure game, the story about sinful soul in search of redemption. <br>The main purpose of the game is to redeem yourself by saving souls of people whose lives you ones ruined.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/9a77f237a9afb28ed460fc9beae63e59.poster.avif?t=1602004954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/9a77f237a9afb28ed460fc9beae63e59.webm?t=1602004954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/9a77f237a9afb28ed460fc9beae63e59.mp4?t=1602004954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Main character appears in the underworld after his own death with a great desire to repair the damage he has caused and that gives his soul incredible strength. <br>In the course of the game, a player needs to fight through a number of different worlds, face various monsters created by hate and finally help broken souls to reach a better place.<br>Player learns a story about these people before their death through multiple items, figures out how they are connected and why they ended up in such dark and hopeless world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/ed9ab520c67668ba3f29668d3d002928.poster.avif?t=1602004954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/ed9ab520c67668ba3f29668d3d002928.webm?t=1602004954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/ed9ab520c67668ba3f29668d3d002928.mp4?t=1602004954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058290/extras/6a1076359f9107f187cc43c296b21d77.avif?t=1602004954\" width=610 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gloomy, but atmospheric setting.<br></li><li>Mysterious masked anti-hero.<br></li><li>Surrealism and nightmares are your new friends.<br></li><li>Charon and other mythological characters are waiting to “mingle” with you.<br></li><li>A fascinating story about travelling to personal hell and back.</li></ul>",
